<br>
So rather than <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Elemental Silence</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, the proposed summoned only mezz at 63rd, let me offer:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Name:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Hold Elemental<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Level:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> 63<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Mana:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> 100<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Class:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  Alteration<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Max Duration:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> 48 seconds<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Casting Time:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> 4 seconds<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Recast Time:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Instant<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Actual Effects:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Elemental Target Root<br>
<br>
No mage ever imagined they might ever mezz.<br>
On the other hand, <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>every</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> mage in their secret heart covets root, even if they will not admit it in polite company.<br>
If I am going to have some lame-ass elemental crowd control spell, then I beg you, <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Karana</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, let it be <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> ROOT</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.<br>
<br>
Then, at least it would be fun, and allow magicians to live out their fantasies of having root.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Sage ArchMage Razamatazz Pizzazz</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
